bilingual.target: 我们的周年纪念日在八月份。

bilingual.source: He gave her a ruby ring for their anniversary.
bilingual.target: 他在他们的周年纪念日送了她一枚红宝石戒指。

bilingual.source: He gifted her a rubin ring for their anniversary.
bilingual.target: 他在周年纪念日送给她一枚红宝石戒指。

bilingual.source: The company just celebrated its tenth anniversary.
bilingual.target: 这家公司刚刚庆祝了成立十周年周年纪念日。

bilingual.source: They spent their tenth anniversary at a restaurant.
bilingual.target: 他们在餐厅度过了他们的十周年纪念日。

bilingual.source: He composed a special serenade for their anniversary.
bilingual.target: 他为他们的周年纪念日创作了一首特别的小夜曲。

bilingual.source: They received a special gift on their 10th anniversary.
bilingual.target: 他们在第十个周年纪念日收到了一个特别的礼物。

bilingual.source: He gifted her a sapphire bracelet for their anniversary.
bilingual.target: 他在周年纪念日送给她一条蓝宝石手链。

bilingual.source: The launch date coincided with the company's anniversary.
bilingual.target: 发布日期与公司的周年纪念日同时发生。

bilingual.source: The museum is hosting an exhibition to mark the anniversary.
bilingual.target: 博物馆正在举办一个展览来纪念这个周年纪念日。

list.abstract: anniversary（英[ˌænɪˈvɜːsəri]，美[ˌænɪˈvɜːrsəri]），英语单词。做名词用，指周年纪念日、结婚纪念日、建国周年纪念日等。英语短语有silver wedding anniversary（银婚纪念日），例句：It is a bitterly ironic thing to learn on the 20th anniversary of Whiten's classic study.（在怀特的经典研究20周年之际学习，是一件极其讽刺的事情）。 复数为anniversaries。
《anniversary》是由日本组合KinKi Kids演唱的一首歌曲。由Satomi作词，由織田哲郎作曲。收录于KinKi Kids2017年12月6日发行的专辑《The BEST》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. It's almost our anniversary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周年纪念日快到了。

yingyinNormal.en: Happy anniversary, Topanga. You too, Cory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 周年纪念日快乐，托庞嘉。你也是，科瑞 。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's just say it's our anniversary. Is it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这上面写着今天是我们的结婚一周年纪念日。是么？

yingyinNormal.en: Today marks the 80th Anniversary of the Social Security Act.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是《社会保险法案》的80周年纪念日。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, well excuse me for wanting to be with my girlfriend on our anniversary, boy what an ass am I.
yingyinNormal.zh: 原谅我只想在周年纪念日跟女朋友在一起，老天，我真是混蛋。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh what? Is she gonna cancel on me again? How can she do this? Doesn't she know it's our anniversary?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她又要爽约了？她怎么可以这样？我们的周年纪念日怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yes. According to the Relationship Agreement, on the anniversary of our first date, he must take me to a nice dinner, ask about my day and engage in casual physical contact that a disinterested onlooker might mistake for intimacy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然有，根据恋爱协议，我们的首次约会周年纪念日，他得带我去吃顿好的，关心我那天的生活琐事，然后对我做出一些肢体接触，是让旁观者都觉得我们很亲密的那种哦。

yingyinNormal.en: I was not flirting. And on your anniversary, for shame.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没在打情骂俏。还在纪念日当天，丢脸！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it's more of an anniversary. The 30th anniversary of our game, actually.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只是周年庆典啦，实际上是我们游戏30周年纪念。

yingyinNormal.en: Happy anniversary. An emanator.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周年快乐。这是台投射成像仪。

yingyinNormal.en: There she is. Hi, mi amor. Happy anniversary! Happy anniversary, honey. I hope you like this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在这。亲爱的，结婚纪念日快乐。你也是，亲爱的，我希望你喜欢这个。

yingyinNormal.en: You're not going to say anything? On our 35th wedding anniversary?
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我们35周年派对上，你不致词吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I'm gonna go too. You know Pheebs, it's kinda our anniversary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好耶，我也要去。菲比，这是我俩的纪念日。

yingyinNormal.en: I just had the worst anniversary ever. I doubt that. Tell her about us last year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最烂的周年庆！才不是呢，莫妮，给她讲讲我们去年怎么过的周年。

yingyinNormal.en: August fourteenth is the anniversary of the New Deal. I'd like to hit 20,000 by that date.
yingyinNormal.zh: 8月14日是罗斯福新政的纪念日，届时要达到两万。

yingyinNormal.en: It's your parents' anniversary and you're going to talk about their dead pet? The good stuff?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你爸妈的结婚纪念日你要谈一只死狗？那个主题不错吧？

yingyinNormal.en: For our two-week anniversary, he's taking me to his cousin's cabin for the weekend. Cabin of love.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他为了庆祝我们的双周庆，周末要带我去他表哥的小木屋。爱的小屋。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, yeah, in honor of their 35th wedding anniversary, I had a star named after them. That is so cool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了纪念他们结婚35周年，我用他们的名字帮星星取名。那真的太酷了。

yingyinNormal.en: Happy anniversary, Jay! I don't love this tableau. Is that Gloria's gift to me? What is it? I don't know.
yingyinNormal.zh: 结婚纪念日快乐，杰！我不喜欢你这样，这是歌洛莉亚给我的礼物吗？是什么？不知道。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a present for grown-ups. We've bought this for Granny and Grandpa Pig. It's their wedding anniversary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，这是送给大人的礼物。这花瓶是我们要送给猪爷爷猪奶奶的。今天是他们的结婚纪念日。

direction_info.description:

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
